title: Baby Pet Vet Doctor 2.0.5
description:
Baby Pet Vet Doctor is a sweet virtual pet game for Android where you can choose one of four different pets to look after - a puppy, a kitten, lion cub, and tiger cub.

Once you've chosen your pet you can pamper it, give it a bath, treat its injuries, and dress it up. It feels a bit like a mix between Foot Spa and My Talking Tom. It's cute and easy to play and is a great way for young kids to learn how to care for a pet
